WEBVTT

00:00:00.151 --> 00:00:06.087
Bryn Freedman: You're a guy whose company
funds these AI programs and invests.

00:00:06.111 --> 00:00:11.156
So why should we trust you
to not have a bias

00:00:11.180 --> 00:00:14.356
and tell us something really useful
for the rest of us

00:00:14.380 --> 00:00:16.684
about the future of work?

00:00:17.046 --> 00:00:18.537
Roy Bahat: Yes, I am.

00:00:18.561 --> 00:00:21.549
And when you wake up in the morning
and you read the newspaper

00:00:21.573 --> 00:00:25.022
and it says, "The robots are coming,
they may take all our jobs,"

00:00:25.046 --> 00:00:27.577
as a start-up investor
focused on the future of work,

00:00:27.601 --> 00:00:29.918
our fund was the first one to say

00:00:29.942 --> 00:00:32.252
artificial intelligence
should be a focus for us.